00:02:01.496 --> 00:02:09.515
The glorious church is rising up and getting a backbone, saying, 'No more, Satan! Thus far and no further.

00:02:09.516 --> 00:02:40.634
You will not do any more damage as long as we're here.'That video I did yesterday was really long, but I had an urgency—a prayer urgency—praying for the inauguration coming on the 20th because the enemy is trying to raise his head like that whack-a-mole; you hit it in the head right now.

00:02:40.635 --> 00:02:47.208
